{"tid":2274614,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"終於拉到人！ - 高慧然","createTime":"2020-11-06T14:07:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T14:10:56.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"824383f891ba61d1a3b29cc1d79d19539854ae63","tid":2274614,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T14:07:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201106/OZOBDQWN2BHO7JPFIEPGQDWUCQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201106%2FOZOBDQWN2BHO7JPFIEPGQDWUCQ%2F&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9okJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=b5f72951\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201106%2FOZOBDQWN2BHO7JPFIEPGQDWUCQ%2F&h=40c9043c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201106/OZOBDQWN2BHO7JPFIEPGQDWUCQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n終於拉到人！ - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/aXVHxmchDvshbIoG1d09umgtV0g=/862x555/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/27EKYWU5ZJF4TJHP62J4J7BLDY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FaXVHxmchDvshbIoG1d09umgtV0g%3D%2F862x555%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F27EKYWU5ZJF4TJHP62J4J7BLDY.png&h=f7db7a46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n721事件在發生一年零三個半月之後，重案組終於拉到人，並刑事起訴疑犯。不過，該疑犯並非對西鐵車廂及車站乘客實施無差別恐怖襲擊的恐襲份子，而是嘗試調查事件真相的記者及編導。<br />\n<br />\n因721事件被捕的是香港電台《鏗鏘集》編導蔡玉玲，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n721事件不只是香港警隊的污點，更已經成為整個香港政府碰觸不得的禁區，事發當晚報警電話無人接聽，巿民被白衣人手持武器追打得不到任何警察協助，亦有警員目睹大批白衣人手持攻擊性武器聚集卻無動於衷。<br />\n<br />\n721事件會不會有真相，甚麼時候才會有真相，警黑有沒有勾結，或者永遠成為懸案，令人狐疑。<br />\n<br />\n傳媒工作者為甚麼要設法調查事件真相，不正是因為警隊沒有盡其本份嗎？蔡玉玲固然違反《道路交通條例》，但其動機是甚麼，違法造成的後果又是甚麼，對公眾利益的影響有多大&hellip;&hellip;難道不足令執法機構行使酌情權嗎？不捉暴徒，但捉揭露真相的傳媒人，也難怪巿民會質疑警隊在此事件中扮演的角色。"},{"pid":"f45dea7bf3d874a9e1b37fca76942c04b337bcab","tid":2274614,"uid":33099,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T14:10:56.000Z","msg":"錯<br />\n<br />\n個記者係完全無犯法"}]}